SUBENT        A0045001   20260126   20260317   20260317       A129
BIB                 14         35
TITLE      19F(He3,p)21Ne reaction mechanism below Coulomb
           barrier
AUTHOR     (I.I.Zalyubovsky,V.D.Sarana,S.A.Pismenetsky)
INSTITUTE  (4UKRKHU)
REFERENCE  (J,PKL,2,79,1975) Main reference, in Russian only.
           (R,JINR-P15-7971,1974) Communication of the Joint
           Institute for Nuclear Research, Dubna, 1974 (in
           Russian). Preliminary results.
FACILITY   (VDG,4ZZZDUB)
METHOD     (EXTB,BCINT)
SAMPLE     Thin target-calcium fluoride of 40-80 ug/cm2 thick
           on thin (~10 ug/cm2) carbon backing or thick (~35 mu)
            nickel backing. Thin targets were used in elastic
           scattering for monitor reaction.
DETECTOR   (SILI) Five solid-state Si(Li) detectors on rotating
           platform. Sixth detector at 90. degr. was used for
            monitor purpose.
MONITOR    (9-F-19(HE3,EL)9-F-19,,DA)
MONIT-REF  (,G.M.Matous+,J,PR,152,908,1966)
ERR-ANALYS (ERR-1) Relative uncertainty includes:
            - Statistical error (3.-7.)%;
            - Error of identification of photopeak (2.-3.)%;
            - error of background, approximately 2%.
STATUS     (TABLE) Tables were received from the authors.
           Similar data are given in Tbls 1-3
           (APRVD) By V.D.Sarana.
ADD-RES    (ANGD)
HISTORY    (19800124C)
           (20080609A) BIB section updated.
            Corrections were made according to new EXFOR rules.
           (20140224A) SD: Volume of the ref. corrected. SAMPLE
           moved to Subent 1; MONITOR/MONIT-REF were added;
           BIB updated in Subents 002-007.
           (20260126A) SD: Corrections in all Subents.
           Subents 002-004 and 005-007 were merged.
ENDBIB              35
